OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FTrial dates have been set for
OL,7,Fdefendants, including former mayor of
OL,8,FLiverpool Joe Anderson, charged as
OL,9,Fpart of an investigation into city
OL,10,Fcouncil corruption.
OL,12,FThe 67-year-old and co-defendants,
OL,13,Fincluding former politician Derek
OL,14,FHatton and an ex-director and
OL,15,Fassistant director of Liverpool City
OL,16,FCouncil, appeared at Preston Crown
OL,17,FCourt on Friday.
