OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FAnderson, who was the city's elected
OL,7,Fmayor from 2012 to 2021, is charged
OL,8,Fwith bribery, misconduct in a public
OL,9,Foffice and conspiracy to commit
OL,10,Fmisconduct in a public office.
OL,12,FThe former Labour politician, of
OL,13,FKnotty Ash in Liverpool, is alleged to
OL,14,Fhave sent or arranged to have sent
OL,15,F"threatening letters" to himself.
