OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FThe defendants were charged as part of
OL,7,FOperation Aloft, launched by
OL,8,FMerseyside Police to look into the
OL,9,Fawarding of commercial and business
OL,10,Fcontracts from the council between
OL,11,F2010 and 2020.
OL,13,FAnderson is also accused of conspiring
OL,14,Fwith his son David Anderson, 37, and
OL,15,Fthe council's former assistant
OL,16,Fdirector of highways and planning
OL,17,FAndrew Barr, 51, to arrange special
OL,18,Faccess in a manner to benefit David
OL,19,FAnderson and his company SSC. He did
OL,20,Fnot enter pleas to the charges on
OL,21,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
