OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FHatton, of Aigburth, Liverpool, who
OL,7,Fwas deputy council leader and part of
OL,8,FLabour's militant faction in the
OL,9,F1980s, pleaded not guilty to offering
OL,10,Fa bribe. The 77-year-old, wearing a
OL,11,Fpale blue suit, is also charged with
OL,12,Fcounselling orprocuring misconduct in
OL,13,Fa public office but did not enter a
OL,14,Fplea to the charge.
