OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FHis wife Sonjia Hatton, 49, of
OL,7,FAigburth, did not enter a plea to a
OL,8,Fcharge of misconduct in a public
OL,9,Foffice. She is accused of providing
OL,10,Fand seeking confidential council
OL,11,Finformation over matters of commercial
OL,12,Fand business use to Mr Hatton's
OL,13,Fcontacts and to his business dealings.
OL,15,FThe five defendants are due to stand
OL,16,Ftrial on October 5 2026, with the case
OL,17,Fexpected to last 15 weeks.
