OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FJulian Flanagan, 53, and Paul
OL,7,FFlanagan, 71, both of Knowsley, who
OL,8,Ffounded construction business The
OL,9,FFlanagan Group, pleaded not guilty to
OL,10,Fconspiracy to bribe. They are alleged
OL,11,Fto have conspired with each other to
OL,12,Fbribe Kavanagh and Cook between
OL,13,FNovember 2015 and September 2020 by
OL,14,Fgiving them financial or other
OL,15,Fadvantage, including building,
OL,16,Fdecoration or maintenance work, in
OL,17,Freturn for improper performance by
OL,18,FKavanagh in his employment by the
OL,19,Fcouncil.
