OL,3,CTrial date set for former Liverpool
OL,4,Cmayor and co-defendants
OL,6,FJames Shalliker, 38, of Downholland,
OL,7,FLancashire, and Adam McClean, 54, of
OL,8,FWoolton, are both alleged to have
OL,9,Fconspired with another man, Mark
OL,10,FDoyle, to bribe Kavanagh and Cook with
OL,11,Fcash, the use of storage, vehicles or
OL,12,Fvehicle parts and building work. Both
OL,13,Fpleaded not guilty to conspiracy to
OL,14,Fbribe.
OL,16,FA trial for the six defendants was
OL,17,Ffixed for February 23 next year and is
OL,18,Fexpected to last around 12 weeks.
